# Representation of schema for SDD node with k children
# Nodes
# Root
n r    200 550 e=fillcolor l=$\hat{\mathbf{u}}$
# Sum nodes
n w1   200 500 l=$\lor^{\textsf{s}}$
n w2   300 400 l=$\lor^{\textsf{s}}$
n wkm1 500 200 l=$\lor^{\textsf{s}}$
# Product nodes
n v1   100 400 l=$\land^{\textsf{p}}$
n v2   200 300 l=$\land^{\textsf{p}}$
n vkm1 400 100 l=$\land^{\textsf{p}}$
n vk   600 100 l=$\land^{\textsf{p}}$
