n pkm1 440  25 e=fillcolor l=$\hat{\mathbf{p}}_{k-1}$
n sk   560  25 e=fillcolor l=$\hat{\mathbf{s}}_{k}$
n pk   640  25 e=fillcolor l=$\hat{\mathbf{p}}_{k}$
# Edges
# Between operators
e w1 v1
e w1 w2
e w2 v2
e w2 w3
e w3 wkm2 t=l
e wkm2 wkm1
e wkm1 vkm1
e wkm1 vk
